latestPosts.caption:
I’ve designed countless pieces over the years — each meant to make someone feel seen.
This time, I turned the lens inward.

Four looks. One journey.
Not to model. Not to influence. 

But to wear what I created, for myself — with no brief, no briefings, just instinct.

Over the next few days, I’ll be sharing pieces that felt like extensions of my own energy.
Designed by me. Worn by me.
Because sometimes, the most honest story is the one you don’t cast.

#WornByTheMaker #DishaPatilCouture #PersonalCouture #DesignerInFocus #QuietLuxury #MadeByHer #ModernMuse

Do you like the muse 😉
